ProbesetGenotypeEngine.h File Reference

Core routines for probeset-genotype binaries. By separating the command line parsing form the computation we allow a GUI application to share the core computation once setting up the option class. To run the algorithm setup the Options class appropriately for a particular run (i.e. specify files and parameters) then call probesetGenotype() to perform analysis. More...

Detailed Description

Core routines for probeset-genotype binaries. By separating the command line parsing form the computation we allow a GUI application to share the core computation once setting up the option class. To run the algorithm setup the Options class appropriately for a particular run (i.e. specify files and parameters) then call probesetGenotype() to perform analysis.
